# NewsWave 🌊
> A sleek, dark-themed news website powered by NewsAPI

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
newswave/
├── index.html              ← Home page
├── css/
│   └── style.css           ← Main stylesheet
├── js/
│   └── main.js             ← Core logic (API, scroll, pill nav)
└── authentication/
    ├── login.html          ← Login page
    ├── signup.html         ← Sign up page
    ├── auth.css            ← Auth stylesheet (shared)
    └── auth.js             ← Auth form validation logic
```

---

## ⚡ Quick Setup

### 1. Add your NewsAPI key

Open `js/main.js` and replace the placeholder on line 10:

```js
const CONFIG = {
  API_KEY: "YOUR_NEWSAPI_KEY_HERE",   // ← paste your key here
  ...
};
```

Get a free key at: https://newsapi.org

### 2. Open the project

Just open `index.html` in a browser.

> **Note:** NewsAPI free tier only allows requests from localhost.
> For production, you'll need a backend proxy to hide your API key.

---

## 🎨 Features

### Navigation
- **Pill navbar** — Fixed at the top, never changes colour. Contains category links: Top, Tech, Sports, Entertainment, Business, Science, Health.
- **Glass navbar** — Sits below the pill bar. Transparent when at the top, activates glass blur/colour when scrolling. Tint colour adapts to the current section.

### Home Page
- Animated hero with ambient orb background
- Featured article card (pulled from API)
- Breaking news ticker (auto-scrolling)
- Responsive 3-column news grid
- Skeleton loading states
- Load More pagination
- Search overlay (keyboard shortcut: click the search icon)
- Mobile hamburger menu

### Authentication
- Login page with email + password validation
- Signup page with:
  - Name fields
  - Password strength meter
  - Confirm password matching
  - Terms checkbox
- Social login buttons (Google, GitHub — wire up OAuth)
- Forgot password flow
- Form alert messages (success / error)

---

## 🔧 Customisation

### Change default country
In `js/main.js`:
```js
COUNTRY: "in",   // "us", "gb", "au", etc.
```

### Change categories in pill bar
In `index.html`, edit the `.pill-link` elements.

### Connect real auth
In `authentication/auth.js`, replace `simulateApiCall()` with your actual backend, Firebase, Supabase, or Auth0 calls.

---

## 🌐 API Notes

- NewsAPI free tier: 100 requests/day, localhost only
- For deployment: use a serverless function (Vercel, Netlify) to proxy API requests and keep your key safe.